%% Diagram: cache-invalidation-paths
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant CMS as CMS / PIM
    participant App as App / SSR origin
    participant CDN as CDN edge<br/>(Fastly / Cloudflare / Vercel)
    participant Cache as Edge cache
    participant U as User

    Note over App,Cache: Tag responses on read
    U->>CDN: GET /p/123
    CDN->>App: cache miss
    App-->>CDN: HTML + Surrogate-Key:<br/>product-123 collection-shoes price-eur
    CDN->>Cache: store keyed by URL,<br/>indexed by tags
    CDN-->>U: 200 HTML

    Note over CMS,Cache: Soft purge on write
    CMS->>App: webhook: product 123 updated
    App->>CDN: POST /purge by tag<br/>product-123
    CDN->>Cache: mark entries stale<br/>(soft purge)
    Cache-->>CDN: ack

    U->>CDN: GET /p/123
    CDN-->>U: stale HTML (immediate)
    CDN->>App: revalidate in background
    App-->>CDN: fresh HTML + new tags
    CDN->>Cache: replace entry